snippet.title: Flyff Universe - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Flyff Universe (Fly For Fun) is a cross-platform 3D Browser MMORPG. No download, playable on PC, Mac and Mobile!

🔻 PLAY FLYFF UNIVERSE
Play for free now: https://universe.flyff.com/play
